flowchart TD
    Start[Start Planning Context] --> ReadContext[Read XX-CONTEXT.md & METHODOLOGY.md]
    ReadContext --> ProposePlans[Planner Agent Proposes Plans]
    ProposePlans --> ReviewPlans[Plan Checker Evaluates]
    ReviewPlans --> IssuesCheck{Issues Found?}
    IssuesCheck -- Yes: BLOCKER/WARNING --> Revise[Send Issues to Planner for Revision]
    Revise --> ProposePlans
    IssuesCheck -- No: INFO or PASSED --> OutputPlans[Generate XX-YY-PLAN.md Files]
    OutputPlans --> End[End Planning]
    
    subgraph Spike Investigation
        SpikeCheck{Needs Research?}
        SpikeCheck -- Yes --> CreateSpike[Create SPIKE-NNN]
        CreateSpike --> Investigate[Research & Prototype]
        Investigate --> SpikeResults[Generate SPIKE.md]
        SpikeResults -.-> ProposePlans
    end
    
    Start -.-> SpikeCheck
